-- China Selects 272 Megawatts of Solar-Power Projects for State Subsidies
-- B y   B a l d a v e   S i n g h
-- 2010-11-23T07:09:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/china-selects-272-megawatts-of-solar-power-projects-for-state-subsidies.html
China has selected solar power
projects with 272 megawatts of capacity that will be eligible
for subsidies under its Golden Sun program, the ministry of
finance said today in a statement on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Baldave Singh at 
 bsingh35@bloomberg.net  